data.description: Located in the heart of Clermont! One owner since the home was built in the year 2000.  This 4 bedroom, 2 baths home in Skyridge Valley Subdivision can become your home sweet home!  With over 1900 square feet of living space, there is plenty of room to add your personal touch and make this home your sanctuary.  Use your imagination and transform it to suit your personality.  Tile floor throughout, appliances less than 5 years old, roof is 3 years old, sprinkler system.  The second bath was remodeled a few years ago.  Close to shopping, restaurants, hospitals, and other amenities that the City of Clermont offers.    Schedule a showing today!
